                    "description": "High Profile Locaties B.V. is a online multimedia publisher whose main aim is to become the Dutch meeting, event, congress and wedding venue specialist. This is done through the publication of different venue yearbooks, websites, apps and digital newsletters. \n\nHigh Profile Locaties B.V. focuses on both corporate decision makers and influencers such as marketing -, communication - and event managers and bridal couples in order to bring supply and demand together within the Dutch venue market. \n\nBy means of a wide range of publications distributed through subscription and controlled circulation to the target audience High Profile is able to bring together supply and demand, e.g., venues with meeting \u2013 and event planners (www.locaties.nl),  marketing and event managers with inspiring meeting locations (www.inspirerendelocaties.nl) and bridal couples with unique wedding venues (www.toptrouwlocaties.nl).\n\nAs account manager I am primarily responsible for the growth of Locaties.nl and Toptrouwlocaties.nl by developing good relationships with clients and helping them to get more exposure within both the corporate - and wedding market. Besides mine activities as an account manager I am also responsible for maintaining all social media platforms, developing and executing social media campaigns, and then analyzing the results. As a Social Media Manager my job doesn't end when the clock strikes 5 pm...",
